text: Cagpating is an island located in the Philippine island Province of Masbate. It is a very steep island that was denoted in 1919 as being heavily wooded, and the west side of the island has prominent cliffs that are around in height. ==See also== * List of islands of the Philippines ==References== ==External links== * Image of Cagpating island.
